metadata.name: #01 - "ORIGIN"
metadata.description:
- NXSP#01 - "ORIGIN"
- 2048 x 2048 px
- "The Connection Company" is dedicated to serving people suffering from insomnia. After grabbing a ticket, passengers will travel from the origin block where their worries are visualized and visit other people's dreams to spend the long long nights. This piece is the beginning station of the adventure so it's called "ORIGIN".
